<br>
Before you start thinking that I'm trying to get people to use my site instead of these message boards or trying to sell something to you, or trying to tell you what to do, please don't because I'm not at all.<br>
<br>
In fact, I play on Bristlebane and we use EZBoards message boards to reserve and roll for upcoming big-game like Nagafen and Lady Vox and POG. But after it's determined that someone or some guild gets to host a raid, they all use my site to organize it. The site basically takes up where the message board stops. The site supliments your means of reserving raids.<br>
<br>
If you'd like, I can also put a link on the site for those on your server which will direct them right here with instruction that they need to make sure they schedule and reserve their events on these message baords BEFORE they post a raid on my site for organization and planning.<br>
<br>
Anyhow, just wanted to mention it since I don't really promote the site thru regular means. It's mostly word of mouth. (already 7000 users on 37 servers in 400 guilds use it)<br>
<br>
Thanks for reading me. Sorry if this was off topic or unappropriate. I didn't want to be rude to you guys.<br>
<br>
Have fun, enjoy the game.<br>
<br>
